# ===== GENERATING HASHED REQUIREMENTS =====
#
# For production environments, generate hashed requirements:
#
# 1. Install pip-tools:
#    pip install pip-tools
#
# 2. Create requirements.in (without hashes):
#    flask==3.0.0
#    requests==2.31.0
#
# 3. Generate requirements.txt with hashes:
#    pip-compile --generate-hashes requirements.in
#
# 4. Install with hash verification:
#    pip install -r requirements.txt --require-hashes

# ===== UPDATING DEPENDENCIES =====
#
# 1. Check for outdated packages:
#    pip list --outdated
#
# 2. Review changelogs for security fixes
#
# 3. Test updates in development first
#
# 4. Audit after updating:
#    pip-audit

